articles.title: Hackathon Update: Friendship is Magic
articles.description: Have you ever wanted to contribute to greatness? A project that will blow peoples minds? As you read in the title: the theme is friendship! Build something that connects people to one another, additionally yasir has made another announcement the following week to promote the hackathon. Some words from one of our members “Man this hackathon stuff is too long. I don't know if I'll be able to finish my project in time.” But what she does know is
articles.author: Shai Yaish
